zhenwu_sun_002 = { #孫重進 Sun Chongjin or 李存進 Li Cunjin. Son of Sun Quan. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 893.5.20 given name 李存進. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 900 made 永安軍使, 北都知兵馬使. (舊五代史/卷53) In 900.5.31 made 知汾州軍州. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 906.3.28 made 知石州軍州事. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 908.2.5 made 石州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 912.1.22 made 知汾州軍州事. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 914.3.30 made 慈州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 慈州刺史 until 914.12.20, on that day made 沁州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 沁州刺史 until 915.7.15, on that day made 天雄都巡按使. (資治通鑑/卷269) In 919.4.4 made 振武節度使. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 振武節度使 until 922.9.24, on that day killed in battle. (舊五代史/卷29)
	dynasty = zhenwu_sun_dyn #Zhenwu Sun
	name = "Chongjin_name"
	culture = han
	religion = jingxue
	father= zhenwu_sun_001

	trait = education_martial_3
	trait = diligent

zhenwu_sun_003 = { #孫漢韶 Sun Hanshao. Eldest son of Li Cunjin. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 925.12.19 era made 蔡州刺史. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 926 changed surname back to 孫. (舊五代史/卷53) In 927.8.30 once again made 蔡州刺史. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 928.3.25 made 彰國軍節度觀風留後. (孫漢韶墓誌) 彰國軍節度觀風留後 until 929.5.12, on that day his mother died. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 932.2.17 made honorary 利州節度使. (舊五代史/卷43 and 孫漢韶墓誌) In 933.7.18 made 洋州節度使. (舊五代史/卷44) In 934.8.31 made 永平軍節度使. (資治通鑑/卷279) In 938.2.2 made 昭武軍節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 939.7.19 made 山南節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 944.6.23 once again made 山南節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 947.7.21 made 武信節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 954.4.6 once again made 武信節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) 武信節度使 until 955.8.30, on that day died. (孫漢韶墓誌)

wanqiu_fu_004 = { #符彥饒 Fu Yanrao or 李彥饒 Li Yanrao. 曹州刺史 in 926.7.26, on that day pacified a rebellion of 張諫 in 汴州, putting 韋儼 in control. 義成節度使 in 937.7.23.

linpu_zhang_053 = { #張亢 Zhang Kang. Son of Zhang Yuqing. (安陽集/巻47/故客省使眉州防禦使贈遂州觀察使張公墓誌銘) In 1019 Jinshi. (墓誌銘) At some point made 知安肅軍事. (墓誌銘) Later made 知瀛州. (墓誌銘) In 1038 made 涇原路兵馬鈐轄兼知渭州. (墓誌銘) 知渭州 until 1039.5.1, on that day made 鄜延路鈐轄兼知鄜州事. (續資治通鑑長編/卷126) 知鄜州 until 1041.1.28, on that day made 知延州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷129) 知鄜州 until 1042.9.20, on that day made. (續資治通鑑長編/卷133) Later made 涇原路經略安撫招討等使本路都總管兼知渭州事. (墓誌銘) 知瀛州 in 1042.10.22. (續資治通鑑長編/卷137) 知瀛州 until 1042.12.25. (續資治通鑑長編/卷138) In 1044.8.15 made 兼知代州兼河東縁邊安撫事. (續資治通鑑長編/卷151) Later once again made 知瀛州. (宋史/卷324) 知瀛州 until 1047.3.16, on that day made 知渭州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷160) 知渭州 until 1047.9.24, on that day made 知壽州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷161) 知壽州 until 1048.8.14, on that day made 知和州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷164) In 1049 made 知筠州事. (瑞州府志) 知衛州事. (墓誌銘) 知懐州事. (墓誌銘) 知懐衛二州 before 1060.4.10. (續資治通鑑長編/卷191)

(墓誌銘) Later again made 知莫州. (墓誌銘) Later made 知保州. (墓誌銘) Later made 知澶州. (墓誌銘) 榮州防禦使 in 1039.7.5, on that day made 鄜延路副都署. （續資治通鑑長編/卷123） 邕州觀察使 until 1040.6.5, on that day made 中正軍節度使. （續資治通鑑長編/卷127） 中正軍節度使 until 1040.9.14, on that day made 定難節度使. （續資治通鑑長編/卷128）

1404804 = {#任得敬 Ren Dejing. First a Controller-general 通判 at Xi'an 西安州. In 1137 he surrendered to Xi Xia after Xi'an was taken by them. Made a prefect by Quanshun. In 1138 in order to curry a favour with the Emperor he introduced his daughter to the palace. In 1137 she became a concubine and he was made a Defense and Security Commissioner at Jingzhou 靜州防禦使. Due to bribery he rose in ranks at the court and became a high offical. In 1138 he was able to make his daughter an Empress, while he himself because Imperial father-in-law 上國丈爷 and he a Supreme Commander at Jingzhou 都統軍. In 1139 his daughter becomes Empress Dowager, even though the next Emperor is not her biological son. In 1140 as a reward for pacifying the rebellion of Xiao Heda 蕭合達 he is enfeoffed as Duke of Xiping 西平公 and made Supreme Commander of Xiangqing Army 翔慶軍都統軍. In 1143 he pacifies agrarian revolts in Xianzhou and Dingzhou 威州、定州等. In 1147 he conspires to have more say in the government, but is stopped by Wo Daozhong 斡道冲 and other ministers. In 1149 he is made 尚書令 中書令. In 1156 he becomes a Prime Minister 國相 after the death of Chage, his younger brothers Decong a Captain of Palace guards 殿前太尉, Degong Governor of Capital Prefecture Xingqing 興慶府尹. Soon after he forces Renzong to make him Prince of Chu 楚王. In 1165 he build a fortress in Lingzhou and a palace for himself, requests control over Shazhou, Guazhou, Lingzhou and Xiazhou. In 1170 he creates a fief for himself, Renzong is forced to consent and gives Southwestern Circuit 西南路, Xiping 西平府, Lingzhou 靈州 and other provinces to Chu. He asks for recognition from Jin, but is rebuked and instead offers a two-side attack on Jin to Song. However, his plot is discovered and Renzong with the support of Jin captures and executes Ren brothers in 8th month.

(景定建康志/卷13) Later moved to 許州、河陽、徐州 over the span of 6 years. (宋史/卷341) 知明州 until Zhezong's enthronment. (宋史/卷341) Later made 知陳州, but didn't go. (宋史/卷341) In 1087.7.10 made 知陳州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷402)
